lead_paragraph: Fast bowler Mohammad Sami and batsman Sharjeel Khan were added to the Pakistan squad on Tuesday for next month's World Twenty20 in India following injuries to Babar Azam and Rumman Raes.

headline.print_headline: Sami Back as Injury Forces Changes in Pakistan T20 Squad
